# Reharm-tactics bulk generated artifacts (all rebuildable from scripts)
#   - 11,160 variation JSONs   : python -m trefoil.reharm.selector --all
#   - 11,160 .mid + .ly        : python -m cli.reharm_render --all
#   - 57,280 fragments         : python -m cli.reharm_cut --all
#   - corpus catalog + shape library : their own generators
# NOTE: per-tactic MIDI demos under data/reharm/tests/<slug>/ are TRACKED —
# they are survey fixtures for the tablet A/B evaluation UI, not bulk output.
data/reharm/variations/
data/reharm/renders/
data/reharm/fragments/
data/reharm/catalog.json
data/reharm/shape_library.json

